extends base

block content
  table(align='center' style='\
  background-color: #fff;\
  /* box-shadow: 0px 1px 22px 0px #3333331a; */\
  text-align: center;\
  border-radius: 0;\
  width: 600px;\
  margin: 0px auto 0px;\
  ')
    // CONTENT HEADER STARTS
    tr(style="width: 600px;")
      td(style='\
      font-weight: 700;\
      font-size: 1.6rem;\
      color: #060016;\
      padding: 0 30px 10px;\
      width: 600px; \
      ')
        | 🚀 Welcome! Let's Dive In!
    // CONTENT HEADER ENDS
    // CONTENT BODY STARTS
    tr(style='text-align: left; color: #4f4f4f;')
      td(style='padding: 0 30px; font-size: 1rem;')
        p Hi #{firstName},

        p Welcome to PathNest! 🎈 We’re thrilled to have you onboard as we help you unlock your child’s potential.

        p ✨ What’s next?

        ul
          li Complete your child’s profile to get tailored career insights. 
          li Dive into their personalized recommendations based on their personality and aptitudes.

        p 💡
          | 
          strong Pro Tip: 
          | Add your partner to your child’s profile! They’ll get to see career insights, but don’t worry, only you can update the profile details.

        p(style="margin-bottom: 0;") 👩‍💻 Need help? We’re just a click away. Here’s to bright futures and exciting paths ahead! 🚀
        
    tr(style='text-align: left; color: #4f4f4f')
      td(style='padding: 0 30px; font-size: 1rem;')
        p
          | Warm regards,
          br
          | The PathNest Team.
          
    tr(style='text-align: left; color: #4f4f4f')
      td(style='padding: 0 30px; font-size: 1rem;')
        p(style='padding-bottom: 35px')
          | ⚠️ 
          i
            strong Disclaimer: 
            | PathNest offers great career guidance but isn't 100% perfect. It's a fun tool to spark conversations and help your child explore possibilities based on their strengths.
    
        
    // CONTENT BODY ENDS